## Description {#details}

Detailed information about the processor of the system that generated this minidump.

Its interpretation depends on the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/minidump/#a22d0c83eebe4572c93fdb8a82a5e1840">ProcessorArchitecture</a> enum.
